Module jdk.management

Package jdk.crac.management

package jdk.crac.management
This package contains a management interface of the CRaC functionality in the Java virtual machine. The jdk.crac.management API doc is https://crac.github.io/openjdk-builds/javadoc/api/jdk.management/jdk/crac/management/package-summary.html.
